I have very crippling social anxiety starting from childhood where I was selectively mute. I never talked and had few friends. Growing up, I was extremely unfortunate looking and an easy target for bullies. I was called every name in the book. I was made to feel less than and I soon internalized it. I hate myself. It‚Äôs not even about the kids that bullied me (I forgave them) it‚Äôs just that all of that programming is engrained so deeply into my psyche. For a long time, I operated from that place. It‚Äôs gotten to the point where if someone shows interest in me (platonic or romantic), I immediately look for ways to confirm that they‚Äôre bad and distance myself. I think that I might have PTSD??

On top of that, my dad was abusive and I witnessed a lot of domestic violence. I just feel like a failure. I went to college and graduated four years ago but I can‚Äôt find employment (out of work for 9 months), I‚Äôm 27 and live at home, I am socially isolated and inept. I haven‚Äôt met any social milestones. Everyone criticizes me harshly for who I am as a result. 

I‚Äôve always had problems but no one helped me. I wanted to see a psychiatrist at 16 for my mental issues but my mom mocked me. She didn‚Äôt put me on her insurance plan causing me to be unable to see one later as an adult. My mom has constantly sabotaged me. I lost nearly 80 lbs after high school but she kept calling me fat causing me to gain it back. She constantly discourages me from moving out, working, dating, and living a normal life. It‚Äôs like she wants me to be as miserable as she is.

I‚Äôm just stagnant and exhausted at this point. If I reincarnate, I wonder if it will be worse than this??   I wrestle with this but I‚Äôm at a point of just wanting to go home. I want to be with ‚Äúpeople‚Äù that love me for the soul that I am. I never felt that I belonged and the feeling is only magnified.
